    "body": "Following https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/22907#issuecomment-824218296\r\nin order to cleanly add plugins using spack, a good way is to extend \"visit\" so that plugins can be activated in the visit prefix.\r\nAlso, in order to build plugins against a VisIt installed through spack, I added VISIT_INSTALL_THIRD_PARTY=ON\r\nto cmake args - thanks to Kathleen Biagas.\r\n\r\n",
